<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/richard-hermer> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Richard Hermer was appointed Attorney General on 5 July 2024. Richard Hermer KC was called to the Bar in 1993 and he took silk in 2009. He was previously Head of Chambers at Matrix and has served as a Deputy High Court Judge. "@en .
